---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"

import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import {
    nxLinks,
    ocLinks
} from "../data/teachingLinks"

import teacherInClass from "../images/teacher-in-class.png"
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main>
    <Image src={teacherInClass} class="hero-image" alt="A classroom setting with a female teacher in front of a digital whiteboard displaying code, and students at desks with laptops." />
    <section>
      <article>
        <h1>Passion comes with great teacher</h1>
        <p>
          In life, I am driven by two passions: unraveling complex problems
          through code and imparting the skills to others on how to navigate
          such challenges. We all carry the imprint of great teachers from our
          schooling years – individuals who had the alchemy to transmute our raw
          energies into passion and arouse interest in subjects we initially
          found inscrutable or unappealing.
        </p>
        <p>
          For over 6 years, I have been immersed in the realm of teaching and
          coaching, a journey that has seen me mentor developers in diverse
          settings, from online mentoring sessions to classroom environments,
          and expansive MOOCs. My MOOCs, rich with insights and practical
          wisdom, have been the academic companions to thousands of students
          globally.
        </p>
        <p>
          My teaching philosophy is rooted in empowerment. I strive to cultivate
          autonomy in my students, encouraging them to think independently
          rather than lean passively on external aid. It's about teaching them
          how to fish, offering them the tools, skills, and confidence to
          navigate the intricate waters of coding independently.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over the years, my exploratory journey in education has woven through
          various teaching modalities. From one-on-one coaching sessions to
          orchestrating classes and designing 8 comprehensive online courses
          with OpenClassrooms, every interaction is an opportunity to ignite
          curiosity, nurture skills, and inspire excellence.
        </p>
      </article>
      <aside>
        <h2>Selected Courses</h2>
        <section>
            <h3>With NX Academy</h3>
            <ul>
                {
                    nxLinks.map(link => (
                        <li>
                            <a href={link.href}>{link.content}</a>
                        </li>
                    ))
                }
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h3>With OpenClassrooms</h3>
            <ul>
                {
                    ocLinks.map(link => (
                        <li>
                            <a href={link.href}>{link.content}</a>
                        </li>
                    ))
                }
            </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
